‌Chapter 12: OSHO Chakra Sounds Meditation This meditation can be done at any time. It uses vocal sounds to open and harmonize the chakras* or energy centers while bringing awareness to them. It can bring you into a deep, peaceful, inner silence either through making your own vocal sounds or by just listening to the music and feeling the sounds within you.
* All chakras lie deep within, rather than on the surface of the body.

